[[Gonyanhatu]] chiumbwa chine mativi matatu nemagonya matatu.

==Mhando dzegonyanhatu==

Muchikamu chino tichataura pamusoro pemarudzi egonyanhatu; mhando dze[[gonyanhatu]] dzinotumidzwa mazita zvichienderana nekupimwa kwemativi uye magonya ari pakati paro. Kune [[gonyanhatu mufanakose]] (equilateral triangle) - iri rine mativi ose akaenza uye gonya nhatu dzose dzakaenzana. Kune [[gonyanhatu mutseyekwa]] (scalene triangle) - iri rine mativi ose ane nhambwe dzakasiyana uye gonya nhatu dzose dzakasiyana. Hazvinei [[gonyanhatu mutseyekwa]] agara nedivi ripi anotaridzika seanorerekera (kana kuwandira) kune rimwe divi nguva dzose. Kune [[gonyanhatu mufanambiri]] (isosceles triangle) - iri rine mativi maviri akaenzana, negonya mbiri dzakaenzana. Kunoitawo [[gonyanhatu yemutwi]] (right-angled triangle) - iyi ine mativi maviri anosvika pahawa ine gonya re 90dhigiri.
